Home has 4 beds/2 full baths and nice size addition on back that has a large bedroom and family room.  Basement is partially finished with another family room area.  Screened in porch which looks out over almost 1/2-acre yard.  One car detached garage.   Home is close to 283, 322, and Hershey Med  Center.
